---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<Layout title="Research — Niklas Jütting" description="Research by Niklas Jütting on geoeconomics, trade, and international economic policy.">
  <main>
    <div class="container page-content">

      <h1 class="page-title">Research</h1>

      <p class="github-note">
        For replication code and data, see my
        <a href="https://github.com/juttingn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="paper-link">GitHub page</a>.
      </p>

      <section class="research-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Master's Thesis</h2>
        <ul class="paper-list">
          <li class="paper-entry">
            <p>
              Jütting, N., 2026,
              <a href={`${base}/thesis.pdf`} target="_blank" class="paper-link">
                Geoeconomic Risk Exposure and Investments: EU firms' response to Russia's invasion of Ukraine
              </a>.
              Master Thesis in International Economic Policy, Sciences Po Paris.
              <a href={`${base}/thesis.pdf`} target="_blank" class="pdf-badge">PDF</a>
            </p>
            <p class="paper-abstract">
              This paper studies the geoeconomic risk exposure of EU firms and estimates
              its impact on investment. It introduces the GRE, a new text-based index
              built from corporate earnings calls that measures geoeconomic risk exposure
              at the firm level. Using Russia's invasion of Ukraine as a shock, it finds
              that highly exposed firms increased investment by 12% following the start of
              the war, with marked differences across sectors. The results suggest that
              geoeconomic risk operates through two channels: one prompting firms to
              diversify away from risky countries, and another that heightens uncertainty
              and thereby dampens investment.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="research-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Policy Work</h2>
        <ul class="paper-list">
          <li class="paper-entry">
            <p>
              Dreher, F., Jütting, N., and Schölermann, H., 2025,
              <a href="https://www.ecb.europa.eu/press/economic-bulletin/focus/2025/html/ecb.ebbox202507_08~8bb10dd42d.en.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="paper-link">
                Hitting record highs: unpacking support for the euro
              </a>.
              ECB Economic Bulletin, Issue 7/2025.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .github-note {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .research-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .paper-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .paper-entry {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .paper-entry:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .paper-entry > p:first-child {
    font-size: 0.975rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .paper-link {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: transparent;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    transition: text-decoration-color 0.15s;
  }

  .paper-link:hover {
    text-decoration-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .paper-title-plain {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .pdf-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: #EEF2FF;
    border: 1px solid #C7D2FE;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
    margin-left: 0.4rem;
    vertical-align: middle;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .pdf-badge:hover {
    background: #E0E7FF;
  }

  .paper-abstract {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 680px;
  }
</style>
